Here's a GDScript function that retrieves a node using its instance ID and returns the value of the `foo` property:

```gdscript
extends Node

var foo = "bar"

func get_foo_from_id(instance_id: int) -> String:
    var inst = instance_from_id(instance_id)
    if inst and inst.has("foo"):
