Here's how to use the put_utf8_string method in a C# context:

```csharp
void PutUtf8String(string value)
{
    // Convert string to UTF-8 bytes
    byte[] utf8Bytes = value.ToUtf8Buffer();
    uint size = (uint)utf8Bytes.Length;

    // Assume stream is an instance of your data stream class
    stream.PutData(BitConverter.GetBytes(size)); // Put size first
    stream.PutData(utf8Bytes); // Then put the UTF-8 string
}

