@export var another_building : PackedScene = null  # Better practice
```

In C#, the concept of preload does not exist as in GDScript, but we can use the ResourceLoader to manage resources efficiently. Preload throughout other languages means loading a resource during the initialization phase while load means loading at runtime. Example implementation: ```csharp
